# VHS tape: capture the knowledge-graph explorer. Run from repo root.
Output docs/_graph.gif
Set Shell bash
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 1560
Set Height 880
Set Padding 12
Hide
Type "/Users/hitensaxena/.cargo/bin/curlyos"
Enter
Sleep 4s
Type "4"
Sleep 4s
Show
Sleep 500ms
Screenshot docs/graph.png
Type "j"
Type "j"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 5s
Screenshot docs/graph-focus.png
Type "q"
